Package servlets

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddUserServlet
    This Servlet class adds a user into the system.
    AssignProfServlet
    This Servlet class assigns a Professor to the CMS system.
    AssignTAServlet
    This Servlet class assigns a Teaching Assistant to the CMS system.
    EditCourseServlet
    This Servlet class is used to edit CMS courses.
    EditInfoServlet
    This Servlet class edits a user's general information.
    ForgotServlet
    This Servlet class is used to recover forgotten credentials.
    LoginServlet
    This Servlet class handles the initial credential authentication to the CMS.
    LogoutServlet
    This Servlet class handles the logoff from the CMS system, and deletes the cookie.
    OfficeHourViewServlet
    This servlet class is used to manage office hours.
    ProxyServlet
    This servlet class handles the Scraping.
    ScheduleViewServlet
    This servlet class implements the view to schedule Courses.
    ServeImage
    This servlet class manages a Blobstore service for the users' pictures.
    UploadImage
    This class uploads images to the Blobstore service.
    UserSearchServlet
    This servlet class manages the research of a user in the CMS sytem.
    ViewCoursesServlet
    This servlet class manages the view of Courses.
